    <div class="faq-a" id="get-blog-content-local-seo-and-social-media-posts-"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Two to 4 emails per month works best for most HVAC companies. Send weekly during peak booking seasons (March through May and September through November). Drop to twice monthly during summer and winter when service demand naturally peaks. Research from our <a href="/blog/blog-frequency-study/">blog frequency study</a> shows that consistent publishing frequency matters more than volume.</p></div></div>
