    <div class="faq-a" id="what-is-a-good-open-rate-for-hvac-email-marketing"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Target 40% to 50% for a well-maintained list. The industry average across all sectors is 43%. Welcome emails perform highest at 83%. Seasonal tune-up reminders typically hit 35% to 45%. If your open rate falls below 25%, clean your list and improve your subject lines.</p></div></div>
