<p>Email marketing for HVAC companies is not optional in 2026. It is the most cost-effective way to retain customers, fill slow seasons, and generate repeat bookings. Start with your existing customer list, set up 2 to 3 automated workflows, and build from there. The companies that email consistently outperform the ones relying on ads alone.</p>
